OL,3,CThousands of children referred to
OL,4,Csocial services in domestic abuse cases
OL,6,FFigures obtained by UTV show that over
OL,7,F5,000 children from across Northern
OL,8,FIreland were referred to social
OL,9,Fservices over concerns regarding
OL,10,Fdomestic abuse in 2024.
OL,12,FIn the latest in episode of our series
OL,13,Fexploring the issue of violence
OL,14,Fagainst women and girls, we explore
OL,15,Fhow children witnessing domestic abuse
OL,16,Fare now recognised under the law.
