OL,6,FWayne Pickering, a teacher at Colaiste
OL,7,FFeirste, said: "You can see here
OL,8,Ftoday, the kids are moving around the
OL,9,Fhall.
OL,11,F"They are agreeing and they are
OL,12,Fquestioning. It is vitally important
OL,13,Fthat they have that chance.
OL,15,F"Maybe they do not understand or they
OL,16,Fhave questions. So, if they can get to
OL,17,Fask those questions and get the
OL,18,Fcorrect answers then we would hope
OL,19,Fthat they will come to the conclusion
OL,20,Fthat everybody is equal because that
OL,21,Fis a fact."
