OL,6,FKerri Todd from Women's Aid has
OL,7,Fdelivered workshops to over 2,000
OL,8,Fstudents since taking up her role in
OL,9,F2024.
OL,11,F"We know that Northern Ireland has one
OL,12,Fof the highest femicide rates in
OL,13,FEurope and we know it is one of the
OL,14,Fmost dangerous places for women and
OL,15,Fgirls to live at the moment. We also
OL,16,Fknow that that does not just happen
OL,17,Fout of nowhere.
OL,19,F"We know it comes from values, belief
OL,20,Fsystems and culture. That starts in
OL,21,Fclassrooms and in the home.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/12
