OL,6,F"That is where we try to come in at,
OL,7,Fto try challenge those values and
OL,8,Fbeliefs and normalised everyday
OL,9,Fsexism," she said.
OL,11,FAs well as challenging young people's
OL,12,Fmindsets, Women's Aid works with
OL,13,Fchildren who have witnessed domestic
OL,14,Fabuse. Those young people are now
OL,15,Frecognised under law.
OL,17,FFigures obtained by UTV reveal that
OL,18,Fmore than 5,000 children from across
OL,19,FNorthern Ireland were referred to
OL,20,Fsocial services over concerns of
OL,21,Fdomestic abuse in 2024.
