OL,6,FThe numbers come as no surprise to
OL,7,FHarriet Long, Children's Services
OL,8,FCoordinator for Belfast and Lisburn
OL,9,FWomen's Aid.
OL,11,FDemand for their services last year
OL,12,Fwas so high that they had to
OL,13,Ftemporarily close their books to new
OL,14,Freferrals.
