OL,6,FIn one Belfast refuge, a childcare
OL,7,Fworker on the frontline says that more
OL,8,Fresources are needed for services that
OL,9,Fhelp children recover from domestic
OL,10,Fabuse.
OL,12,FAnne-Marie Adams from Women's Aid
OL,13,Fsaid: "There are no boundaries where
OL,14,Fdomestic violence is concerned and
OL,15,Fchildren suffer greatly.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G10/12
