OL,3,CThousands of children referred to
OL,4,Csocial services in domestic abuse cases
OL,6,F"What we need to do is put more
OL,7,Fresources into preventative education
OL,8,Fbecause there is more research but
OL,9,Fwhen funding is cut children are the
OL,10,Fones who lose out so that is what we
OL,11,Fneed to do.
OL,13,F"We need to push more. More money
OL,14,Fneeds to be put into these services,
OL,15,Finto preventative education. We can
OL,16,Fonly do so much here at Women's Aid
OL,17,Fbut we are held by funding."
OL,19,FDetails for help and support services
OL,20,Fare available here.
